==English==

===Verb===
{{wikipedia}}
'''to divorce'''  (''transitive'')
# to [[legally]] [[dissolve]] a [[marriage]] between two people
# to end one's own marriage in this way
# to [[separate]] something that was connected
'''to divorce'''  (''intransitive'')
# to [[obtain]] a divorce

====Synonyms====
*(''to legally dissolve a marriage''): [[split up]]
*(''to separate something that was connected''): [[disassociate]], [[disjoint]], [[dissociate]], [[disunite]], [[separate]]

